The perfect combo of tangy and sweet with a kick 🌶 & it’s SO easy to make 🤤 

Add ripe mango to a blender with lime juice, choice of sweetener & water. 
Add fresh mango,chamoy and tajin to popsicle molds (add as much as you’d like) then fill with mango mixture.
Repeat this step until all is filled as many times as you’d like
Freeze & enjoy 🤤
